festival.introText:
90’s Kids, 00’s Lovers, Dancefloor Heroes, and Underground Clubbers...it's time to go back.

Flashback Festival returns for a second year, bringing timeless tunes & fresh vibes to the masses in the city.

Get ready for Manchester’s ONLY outdoor festival celebrating the best dance music from the 90s and 00s!

Flashback Festival is one of the newest festivals in Manchester, with the biggest names from dance music across the globe gathering at this city centre location. They'll be blasting out Old Skool Anthems at what is set to be the hottest festival of summer 2023.

From Euphoric Trance to Clubland Classics, Retro House to Groovin’ Garage and everything in between; the jaw-dropping line up of headliners and pioneers will showcase a full spectrum of dance music royalty from the past 30 years.

 

60+ Artists, 4 Stages + Festival Village

VIP Bar + X-Treme Rides

Official After Party + More

faqs.question: When is Flashback Festival?
faqs.answer: Flashback Festival takes place on Saturday 27th May 2023.

faqs.question: Does Flashback festival have onsite camping?
faqs.answer: No, as Flashback is a one-day festival it is a non camping festival so camping equipment is not needed.

faqs.question: What happens If I bought a ticket and cannot attend?
faqs.answer:
Unfortunately, we can’t issue you with a refund if you can’t make the event due to work commitments or your mates have dropped out. In these circumstances, we advise passing on your tickets privately to avoid losing out on the money spent.

Refunds can only be offered if the event is cancelled or postponed, as agreed upon purchase.

faqs.question: Where is Flashback Festival?
faqs.answer: Flashback Festival will be located at Platt Fields Park, Platt Lane, Manchester M14 5NF.

faqs.question: What does a Flashback Festival VIP ticket include?
faqs.answer:
A VIP ticket includes everything included in a standard ticket plus...

  • VIP lounge
  • Private bar
  • Posh toilets
  • VIP headline DJ's
  • Chill area
  • Q jump

faqs.question: Does Flashback festival have any age restrictions?
faqs.answer: Yes, you must be 18 or over to attend Flashback Festival. You may be asked to show photo ID.
